node_2.subject: Isabella Rodriguez
node_2.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, open Hobbs Cafe at 8:00 am and work at the counter until 8:00 pm, gather party material for the Valentine's Day party at Hobbs Cafe, spread the word about the party to customers and invite them to join at 5:00 pm on February 14th, have dinner at 8:30 pm, spend some time relaxing and watching TV from 9:00 pm to 10:00 pm.
